  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a small saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced zucchini and cook for 3-4 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Add the grated carrots and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced shiitake mushrooms and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Stir in the soy sauce, sesame oil, salt, and black pepper.",
    "To assemble the bowls, place a scoop of cooked brown rice in the bottom of a stone bowl.",
    "Add a variety of the cooked vegetables on top of the rice.",
    "Drizzle the polished vegetable oil over the top of the vegetables.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions and fresh spinach leaves.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
